- Utilize the App Router for improved performance and routing.
- Implement error boundaries to handle both server-side and client-side errors gracefully.
- Leverage tRPC on the server and suspense for efficient data fetching.
- Use Next.js built-in optimizations like image optimization with the Image component.
- Implement server-side rendering for better SEO and initial load times.